	* lib/ssh.c lib/config_file.c lib/Makefile.am lib/gftp.h lib/options.h -
	removed old legacy SSH protocol and option to enable this protocol

	* lib/gftp.h - added GFTP_ERETRYABLE and GFTP_EFATAL error codes

